{"tid":1241762,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"不做逃犯天堂","createTime":"2019-06-18T23:21:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T00:07:26.000Z","uid":100725,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a9cb4224989a40ad45fe2cb239bd5bd159e3bd85","tid":1241762,"uid":100725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T23:21:45.000Z","msg":"第一次開post, 如果講得唔好屌細力啲。<br />\n<br />\n好多中年人廢青同警察嘅朋友仲係講緊如果香港冇逃犯移交條例，將來有強姦犯殺人犯係香港，係市民身邊，唔好到時先叫警察出黎。<br />\n<br />\n陳同佳之亂 (2019)<br />\n-事件成因: 因港男於外地發現戴帽，一怒之下係台灣殺左懷有他人骨肉嘅女朋友，並逃回香港。<br />\n-引起後果: 林奠自稱因為要伸張正義，提出逃犯移交條例修業成例。引起香港人各門各派assemble.. <br />\n<br />\n我諗香港有個大仆街，佢叫陳同佳<br />\n唔理邊一邊都係認同<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ru4TJGPJjjc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRu4TJGPJjjc&d=HhKtR2wUfRZLc9nBt5dK8BYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=6f7cd7af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ru4TJGPJjjc</a><br />\n<br />\n睇完通識堅庭，係咪可以主動建議下政府點樣先可以解決呢個大仆街。<br />\n<br />\n細佬唔識，全能高登仔係唔係可以寫個proposal俾啲議員，證明我地唔係盲反所有關於中國既野。<br />\n<br />\n要支持派所有既立場都冇埋！"},{"pid":"91166c5cb0c9440b989c505e35bbdda5ab62832b","tid":1241762,"uid":76135,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T23:35:01.000Z","msg":"不做中央逃犯300。堵塞漏洞。禁止向大陸貪官發身份証，不讓香港做黑金天堂"},{"pid":"22642a7bdcca8efbabc5906588a3900be362b4da","tid":1241762,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T23:47:02.000Z","msg":"不做逃犯天堂幾時拉689同一哥旗下班謀殺犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd07cc82da9f71544b582835adff5deb08cebdc","tid":1241762,"uid":48154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22642a7bdcca8efbabc5906588a3900be362b4da","tid":1241762,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T23:47:02.000Z","msg":"不做逃犯天堂幾時拉689同一哥旗下班謀殺犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T23:53:30.000Z","msg":"佢講漏咗2個字啫，係不做大陸逃犯天堂，堵塞大陸法律漏洞。"},{"pid":"c56c35d164462f4893e26f1f65e0ef4183ad0e68","tid":1241762,"uid":242630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T23:53:30.000Z","msg":"咁多負皮，證明連登他睇完個標題就亂咁黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceebba1248ee729bda68f54ca38dd38101617cf8","tid":1241762,"uid":100725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c56c35d164462f4893e26f1f65e0ef4183ad0e68","tid":1241762,"uid":242630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T23:53:30.000Z","msg":"咁多負皮，證明連登他睇完個標題就亂咁黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:07:26.000Z","msg":"多謝手足睇左我講乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}